    <h1>Bear Facts</h1>
    <ul>
      <li>The polar bear is the largest land carnivore in the world.</li>
      <li>Bears have an excellent sense of smell, better than dogs.</li>
      <li>
        The sun bear is the smallest bear species, weighing only 60-145 pounds.
      </li>
      <li>
        Bears are intelligent animals that can be taught to perform simple
        tasks.
      </li>
      <li>Grizzly bears can run up to 35 miles per hour.</li>
    </ul>
